    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras/fea76f2a7ffdc0a71ba4d82f5b8b4b7e.avif?t=1763991753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras_big/fea76f2a7ffdc0a71ba4d82f5b8b4b7e.avif?t=1763991753 width=800 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔧 This demo is an older build and no longer reflects the final game. Wishlist to follow its launch of the final game.</strong><br><strong></strong><br><strong>Le Plan Spectral </strong>is a small construction video game.  You, a dead architect, have the role of building castles to house ghosts and restore balance to the world of the living. You are free to design the castles according to your preferences; however, each castle has certain block limitations to ensure the ghosts are welcomed in the best possible conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras/d60d0f804181dbf5caebbc4bcb15494c.avif?t=1763991753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras_big/d60d0f804181dbf5caebbc4bcb15494c.avif?t=1763991753 width=800 height=214 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this small island with your vehicle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build magnificent castles while respecting the block limit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect wood and stones through mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day-night cycle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras/c4cc61b89e7ae7e5f68973caf614cb7d.avif?t=1763991753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324160/extras_big/c4cc61b89e7ae7e5f68973caf614cb7d.avif?t=1763991753 width=800 height=222 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration Mode : </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click to move, select, and enter building mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use keyboard arrows to rotate and move the camera</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Building Mode :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click to place or destroy blocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Right-click to switch blocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press &quot;R&quot; to rotate blocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use keyboard arrows to rotate and move the camera</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing Mode :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wood Fishing : Use keyboard arrows to move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rock Fishing : Use Left Mouse or Press Space to collect</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
